Class HoboNetServer

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.servlet.GenericServlet
      • uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.remote.server.net.MekonNetServer
        • uk.ac.manchester.cs.hobo.remote.server.net.HoboNetServer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, javax.servlet.Servlet, javax.servlet.ServletConfig

    public class HoboNetServer
extends MekonNetServer
    Represents a server-side version of the MEKON frames model, with a bound HOBO object model, and an associated instance store.

    This class is an extension of MekonNetServer, which is designed to be used in combination with the companion server class, MekonNetClient.
